HEADWORD: Intenseness
<hw>In*tense"ness</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>The state or quality of being
intense; intensity; <as>as, the <ex>intenseness</ex> of heat or cold;
the <ex>intenseness</ex> of study or thought.</as></def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

